{"tid":1269729,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"71暴亂夜","createTime":"2019-06-30T16:02:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T21:10:20.000Z","uid":4739,"like":33,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"92db945cf97abbddadc6ee56c0b25f88d0898cf1","tid":1269729,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:02:31.000Z","msg":"套戲已經出左幾年但好戲不妨一睇再睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無巴打知道聽日邊間戲院會有播呢套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n電影TRAILER<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hnK9tv2ZqUA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhnK9tv2ZqUA&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXB4w7aMtX%2B%2FJ%2BUdoe8qorTI%3D&h=9cdc6a23\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hnK9tv2ZqUA</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1971年北愛爾蘭衝突升級，內戰蓄勢待發。新兵加里(積奧干奴 飾)隨隊被緊急派往暴亂的核心地帶，他們剛到埗就遇上強烈反抗的市民，更爆發大型騷亂；加里竟意外被撤退的大隊遺下，手無寸鐵的留在充滿怒火的危險戰場。為爭奪己方利益，激進武裝分子、便衣特工，個個不擇手段；但這一晚他們都有一個共同的目的──搜出這落單新兵，將他置諸死地﹗帶傷的加里在各黨派勢力邊緣遁走，誓要在槍林彈雨中回到摯愛身邊&hellip;"},{"pid":"8de9a3846e88cdbcdff3fc667a512a4156d5a159","tid":1269729,"uid":4739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:21:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"123f9a0951deec0e1e60caeac26d4e1ebcd771b1","tid":1269729,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:22:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0f0a6315545b63520abd0d05333fa42c8957c2a9","tid":1269729,"uid":111720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T16:41:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63217a620c51e339024a7e0a5dd8d8527914d01d","tid":1269729,"uid":82845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T21:10:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}